V0418_01_00_00_0.text:
Target acquired!
I'm taking you out!

V0418_01_00_01_0.text:
Any last words?
Cuz now's the time!

V0418_01_00_02_0.text:
The name's Anna!
Get ready to get blasted!

V0418_01_00_03_0.text: No one can stop my deck when it's speedin' down the tracks!

V0418_01_00_06_0.text:
Yuma!
If I win, you have to take me out...

V0418_01_00_06_1.text:
A-Anyway!
Let's get this Duel started!

V0418_01_00_07_0.text:
What's up, Tori?
I thought I'd crash the party!

V0418_01_00_08_0.text: I won't let you lay a finger on my Yuma!

V0418_03_00_00_0.text:
Scaaaaared?
You better be cuz this Duel is mine!

V0418_03_00_01_0.text:
Ha!
There's no escape for you!

V0418_03_00_04_0.text: You made a big mistake by making me angry!

V0418_05_00_00_0.text:
If you wanted to upset me - it worked!
Now you're gonna pay!

V0418_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0418_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0418_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0418_16_00_00_0.text: This will stop you in your tracks!

V0418_16_00_01_0.text: It's the end of the line!

V0418_21_00_00_0.text: I have no clue how you'll win this!

V0418_21_00_01_0.text:
Woohoo!
Victory is just up ahead!

V0418_28_00_01_0.text:
I did it!
I did it I did it I did it!
I won!

V0418_28_00_02_0.text:
Hah!
Like I'd ever let you defeat me!

V0418_28_00_03_0.text: Gustav Max ran over your mini monsters!

V0418_28_00_04_0.text:
I win, Yuma!
That means you have to be my...

V0418_28_00_05_0.text:
Sorry, Tori.
I'll lay off the accelerator next time.

V0418_29_00_01_0.text:
Sigh...
I shoulda brought a bigger cannon!

V0418_29_00_02_0.text:
Well...
I'll let you off for today.

V0418_29_00_05_0.text:
Just you wait!
I always get my revenge!

V0418_29_00_06_0.text:
Sorry, Yuma.
I wish I won this Duel - like you won my heart.

V0418_33_00_00_0.text: You haven't seen firepower like this before!

V0418_30_00_00_0.text: Are you running away? You chicken!

V0418_30_00_01_0.text: There's nothing you can do but end your turn!

V0418_30_00_02_0.text:
I did it!
I did it I did it I did it!

V0418_34_00_04_0.text: What's the point of using that card?

V0418_34_00_05_0.text: Quit whining and let me Duel!

V0418_34_00_08_0.text: You know how I feel about you. Don't make me say it out loud.

V0418_34_00_09_0.text:
You heard me!
I think you're...

V0418_34_00_10_0.text: "Devoted Love?" Why use a card that lowers my LP to 0?

V0418_35_00_00_0.text:
Leave it to me!
Anna Kaboom will take care of everything!

V0418_35_00_01_0.text:
Yeaaaahhh!
I'll steamroll their whole squad!

V0418_36_00_00_0.text: I'm trusting you, so don't you dare lose!

V0418_36_00_02_0.text: I'd be doing fine if you'd just stay out of my way!

V0418_36_00_03_0.text: It's not like I'm doing this to impress you...

V0418_36_00_04_0.text: Yuma, don't Duel like a total wimp!

V0418_36_00_05_0.text:
I'm no help at all...
I wish I was...

V0418_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Train Connection!

V0418_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Attraffic Control!

V0418_08_00_01_1.text: If you control at least 3 monsters, you can't attack!

V0418_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Revolving Switchyard!

V0418_08_00_03_1.text: I Special Summon a monster, and its Level becomes 10!

V0418_08_00_04_0.text: I send a card to the Graveyard to use Revolving Switchyard!

V0418_08_00_04_1.text: I add a monster in my deck to my hand!

V0418_08_00_05_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Special Schedule!

V0418_08_00_05_1.text: Revive a monster with at least 3000 ATK in Defense Position!

V0418_08_00_06_0.text: Special Schedule activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0418_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Urgent Schedule!

V0418_08_00_07_1.text: It Special Summons two monsters by negating their effects!

V0418_08_00_08_0.text: Urgent Schedule activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0418_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Cyber Summon Blaster!

V0418_08_00_10_0.text: Cyber Summon Blaster fires effect damage right at ya!

V0418_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Fiery Fervor!

V0418_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Barrage Blast!

V0418_08_00_13_1.text: For every Overlay Unit it removes, it destroys a card!

V0418_08_00_14_0.text: Barrage Blast's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0418_08_00_14_1.text: It blasts you with effect damage!

V0418_09_00_00_1.text: Once per turn, I can use an Overlay Unit to deal you damage!

V0418_09_00_01_0.text:
Time for real power!
Gustav Max's effect activates!

V0418_09_00_02_1.text: It uses an Overlay Unit to raise its ATK and DEF!

V0418_09_00_03_1.text: It uses an Overlay Unit to protect a card from effects!

V0418_09_00_04_1.text: I use an Overlay Unit to let a monster attack you directly!

V0418_09_00_05_0.text: When Ironwolf is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0418_09_00_05_1.text: I add a Level 4 Machine-Type monster in my deck to my hand!

V0418_09_00_06_0.text: I play Construction Train Signal Red's effect from my hand!

V0418_09_00_07_0.text: Trolley Olley has an effect that raises ATK!

V0418_09_00_08_0.text: I activate Snow Plow Hustle Rustle's effect from my hand!

V0418_09_00_09_0.text: When Flying Pegasus is summoned, its effect activates!

V0418_09_00_10_1.text: This monster and another monster become the same Level!

V0418_09_00_11_0.text: Ruffian Railcar's effect activates to deal you damage!

V0418_09_00_12_0.text: Ruffian Railcar's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0418_09_00_13_0.text: Derricrane's effect activates from my hand!

V0418_09_00_13_1.text: I can Special Summon it by cutting its ATK and DEF in half!

V0418_09_00_14_0.text: When used as an Overlay Unit, Derricrane's effect activates!

V0418_09_00_14_1.text: It destroys one card on your field!

V0418_09_00_15_0.text: Super Express Bullet Train's effect activates from my hand!

V0418_09_00_16_0.text: Bullet Train's effect activates from my Graveyard this turn!

V0418_09_00_18_0.text: Anger Knuckle's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0418_09_00_19_0.text: Dekoichi the Battlechanted Locomotive's effect activates!

V0418_37_00_00_0.text: Make way for the train that’ll derail your chance to win!

V0418_13_00_00_0.text:
Chug on in!
Superdreadnought Rail Cannon Gustav Max!

V0418_13_00_01_0.text:
Let's go!
Superdreadnought Rail Cannon Juggernaut Liebe!

V0418_13_00_02_0.text:
Goooo!
Number 81: Superdreadnought Rail Cannon Super Dora!

V0418_37_00_01_0.text: This impregnable fortress is the terror of the railways!

V0418_13_00_03_0.text:
Show yourself!
Rank 4 Heavy Armored Train Ironwolf!

V0418_13_00_05_0.text:
Express Train Trolley Olley!
Protect me!

V0418_13_00_06_0.text: Snow Plow Hustle Rustle digs its way to the field!

V0418_13_00_08_0.text: You won't get away from Flying Pegasus Railroad Stampede!

V0418_13_00_09_0.text: I Special Summon Rocket Arrow Express!

V0418_13_00_12_0.text:
Check this out!
Heavy Freight Train Derricrane!

V0418_13_00_13_0.text: Speed on in, Super Express Bullet Train!

V0418_13_00_15_0.text: Here comes Dekoichi the Battlechanted Locomotive!

V0418_26_00_00_0.text: I won't let that happen again!

V0418_26_00_02_0.text: I can take more than that!
